OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCanada sorry for top honour
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgiven to ex-Nazi soldier   
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Canada's Governor General Mary Simon   
OL,6, has apologised for a top Canadian      
OL,7, honour awarded to a former Nazi soldier
OL,8, nearly four decades ago.               
OL,10,FPeter Savaryn, a former chancellor of  
OL,11,Fthe University of Alberta, was given   
OL,12,Fthe Order of Canada in 1987.           
OL,14,FIt has since emerged that Mr Savaryn   
OL,15,Fserved in Nazi Waffen SS units.        
OL,17,FThe apology comes a fortnight after a  
OL,18,Frow in Canada's parliament over an     
OL,19,Finvite to an elderly Ukrainian man who 
OL,20,Fhad fought with Nazi Germany.          
